306
00:19:44,420 --> 00:19:45,380
You never listen to me.

307
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:47,420
You're so hard-headed.

308
00:19:47,900 --> 00:19:49,740
Why would I call you here?

309
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:50,620
To scrub backs?

310
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:52,260
