320
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:20,940
Do you find

321
00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:21,820
my work story that funny?

322
00:20:22,140 --> 00:20:22,660
For real.

323
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:26,940
What?

324
00:20:27,740 --> 00:20:28,540
What kind of job?

325
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:29,580
Where are you working?

326
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:33,380
Take a look.

327
00:20:36,780 --> 00:20:37,700
