336
00:20:52,060 --> 00:20:52,780
Please.

337
00:20:52,780 --> 00:20:53,500
I know you.

338
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,780
With your work experience,

339
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:57,180
the most you could do

340
00:20:58,100 --> 00:20:59,060
