341
00:20:59,060 --> 00:20:59,900
or a clothing salesperson.

342
00:21:00,180 --> 00:21:01,100
And Project Manager?

343
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:03,380
Don't mess up your company.

344
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:07,500
Had I known your attitude,

345
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,540
