360
00:21:32,220 --> 00:21:33,060
Leave right now!

361
00:21:33,220 --> 00:21:33,780
Sorry.

362
00:21:34,380 --> 00:21:35,100
Sit down.

363
00:21:35,780 --> 00:21:36,500
I'm sorry.

364
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:37,380
Sorry.

365
00:21:37,860 --> 00:21:38,380
Sit down.

366
00:21:38,940 --> 00:21:39,540
I'm sorry.

367
00:21:39,940 --> 00:21:40,500
Sit down.

368
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:44,140
This is for you.

369
00:21:44,140 --> 00:21:44,500
Eat.

370
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:45,140
To show my respect for you.

371
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:50,500
Come in.

372
00:21:55,140 --> 00:21:55,460
Come.

373
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:56,780
Give me your bag.

374
00:21:56,780 --> 00:21:57,300
Leave it there.

375
00:21:59,740 --> 00:22:00,580
Have a look around.

376
00:22:00,740 --> 00:22:01,060
Okay.

377
00:22:14,420 --> 00:22:15,660
You read aviation books too?

378
00:22:16,460 --> 00:22:17,900
I read all sorts of things.

379
00:22:18,820 --> 00:22:21,460
These books were posted from France.

380
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:27,300
What are you looking at?

381
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:32,940
Do you remember when you moved in,

382
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:35,660
