383
00:22:37,580 --> 00:22:37,940
Hello.

384
00:22:37,940 --> 00:22:39,900
Mr. Feng, Ms. Tan has moved in.

385
00:22:40,140 --> 00:22:41,420
Okay, I've seen.

386
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:42,740
The Velvet were placed as well?

387
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:44,500
Yes, everything is set.

388
00:22:44,820 --> 00:22:45,540
Alright, thank you.

389
00:22:45,860 --> 00:22:46,460
You're welcome.

390
00:23:02,620 --> 00:23:03,140
How did you know?

391
