395
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:36,300
It's a pity.

396
00:23:36,860 --> 00:23:38,460
The person who comes here the most

397
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:39,940
is Wang Zeyuan.

398
00:23:42,740 --> 00:23:43,500
Feng Rui,

399
00:23:44,460 --> 00:23:45,740
sounds like

400
