401
00:23:48,380 --> 00:23:49,580
I'm worried about you.

402
00:23:50,740 --> 00:23:51,420
I'm fine.

403
00:23:51,420 --> 00:23:52,180
Don't worry.

404
00:23:52,660 --> 00:23:53,300
Right now,

405
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:55,620
we should be worried
about your mom the most.

406
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:00,460
Right.

407
00:24:01,420 --> 00:24:01,900
So,

408
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:04,620
have you figured out how to face Le?

409
00:24:07,140 --> 00:24:08,140
Since I found out

410
00:24:08,620 --> 00:24:10,020
he is my child,

411
00:24:10,180 --> 00:24:11,540
I've thought more than once

412
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:15,060
about how to tell him

413
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:16,180
that I am his mother.

414
00:24:19,060 --> 00:24:20,420
Do you think he'll accept it?

415
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:22,660
I don't know.

416
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:25,140
But what's meant to happen will happen.

417
00:24:26,780 --> 00:24:27,220
We'll

418
00:24:27,780 --> 00:24:28,540
face this together.

419
00:24:31,260 --> 00:24:31,740
Should I

420
00:24:32,020 --> 00:24:32,820
tell him for you?

421
00:24:32,940 --> 00:24:33,260
No.

422
00:24:34,580 --> 00:24:35,580
I have to do it myself.

423
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:38,980
Okay.

424
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:40,780
By the way,

425
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:42,660
what's going on with Siting?

426
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:43,980
She's been unreachable lately.

427
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:45,420
I don't know.

428
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:49,220
Oh no,

429
00:24:50,460 --> 00:24:53,060
my guess was right after all.

430
00:24:54,220 --> 00:24:54,700
It's fine.

431
00:24:56,060 --> 00:24:56,620
It's good.

432
00:24:56,900 --> 00:24:59,460
Put all your energy into your work

433
00:25:00,180 --> 00:25:01,740
and take your career to the next level.

434
00:25:01,980 --> 00:25:02,300
Come on,

435
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:06,900
let's toast to my return to work.

436
00:25:10,100 --> 00:25:10,900
Nothing else, right?

437
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:11,980
I'm going back to the company.

438
00:25:15,500 --> 00:25:16,060
So you won't eat? Fine.

439
00:25:16,060 --> 00:25:16,980
I'll eat it myself.

440
00:25:19,180 --> 00:25:19,660
It's all mine.

441
00:25:20,860 --> 00:25:21,700
No one's to celebrate with me.

442
00:25:21,860 --> 00:25:22,740
I'll celebrate by myself.

443
00:25:23,180 --> 00:25:24,060
What's so great about that?

444
00:25:26,260 --> 00:25:26,700
Grandma.

445
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:28,620
Grandma.

446
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:31,980
What are you thinking about?

447
00:25:32,820 --> 00:25:34,260
I've been calling you several times.

448
00:25:34,740 --> 00:25:35,580
Have you?

449
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:37,580
Look, almost no apple left to eat.

450
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:56,340
You're back.

451
00:25:56,420 --> 00:25:56,740
Le!

452
00:25:56,860 --> 00:25:57,340
Dad,

453
00:25:58,140 --> 00:25:58,780
