454
00:26:00,100 --> 00:26:01,060
I bought you some pastries.

455
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:04,780
You left without a word

456
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:06,140
and came back without one.

457
00:26:06,580 --> 00:26:07,580
About the comic con you promised,

458
00:26:07,580 --> 00:26:09,180
I had to go with Mr. Lu.

459
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:10,820
Sorry.

460
00:26:11,060 --> 00:26:12,460
I had an urgent matter to deal with.

461
00:26:13,540 --> 00:26:14,860
How did it go?

462
00:26:16,460 --> 00:26:17,060
It's almost done.

463
00:26:19,820 --> 00:26:20,860
As long as it's sorted out.

464
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:24,740
Le,

465
00:26:26,020 --> 00:26:26,700
stop playing games.

466
00:26:27,460 --> 00:26:28,300
Do your homework in your room.

467
00:26:29,060 --> 00:26:29,580
Take the pastries with you.

468
00:26:29,740 --> 00:26:30,140
Go to your room.

469
00:26:32,740 --> 00:26:32,940
Here,

470
00:26:33,260 --> 00:26:33,980
take this apple.

471
00:26:34,900 --> 00:26:35,220
Hold it tight.

472
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:40,220
Finish your homework before you eat.

473
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:42,140
The pastries are yours.

474
00:26:56,060 --> 00:26:56,900
Who did you go with?

475
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:00,780
Aren't you going to say anything?

476
00:27:02,860 --> 00:27:04,940
When will you register
your marriage with Peiyan?

477
00:27:05,780 --> 00:27:06,820
You missed it last week.

478
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:08,380
I checked it.

479
00:27:08,980 --> 00:27:09,980
Tomorrow is quite suitable.

480
00:27:09,980 --> 00:27:10,700
Peiyan and I...

481
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:11,180
How about...?

482
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:12,020
We've broken up.

483
00:27:18,940 --> 00:27:19,700
What did you just say?

484
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:24,460
Thanks to Peiyan's decision,

485
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:27,540
I didn't get lost in this mistake.

486
00:27:27,980 --> 00:27:28,820
It gave me the chance...

487
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:30,580
What do you take marriage for?

488
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:32,180
A child's game?

489
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:47,180
Just because of Tan Siting?

490
00:27:50,860 --> 00:27:51,820
Marriage

491
00:27:51,820 --> 00:27:53,580
should not be built upon lies.

492
00:27:54,340 --> 00:27:55,660
It's been 12 years.

493
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:58,940
Twelve years, and you can't move on.

494
00:28:00,380 --> 00:28:02,100
What spell did she put on you?

495
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:05,340
To avoid feeling guilty toward her,

496
00:28:05,820 --> 00:28:07,940
you hurt someone who loves you more.

497
00:28:07,980 --> 00:28:09,980
Aren't you guilty toward Yan?

498
00:28:10,140 --> 00:28:12,020
Allowing this to keep escalating

499
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:13,580
will truly hurt her in the end.

500
00:28:14,900 --> 00:28:15,420
Think about it.

501
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:17,260
If we hadn't broken up,

502
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:18,860
or if she knows the truth

503
00:28:18,980 --> 00:28:19,740
after we get married

504
00:28:20,060 --> 00:28:21,500
and become husband and wife,

505
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:23,140
that will be betraying her.

506
00:28:23,700 --> 00:28:25,700
I want to marry with true love.

507
00:28:25,860 --> 00:28:26,740
I don't want a marriage

508
00:28:26,740 --> 00:28:27,780
like that between you and Dad.

509
00:28:29,660 --> 00:28:31,740
Don't comment on my marriage.

510
00:28:32,620 --> 00:28:33,380
We

511
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:34,540
may not love each other,

512
00:28:35,580 --> 00:28:36,900
but we have feelings.

513
00:28:42,740 --> 00:28:44,380
You've disappointed me.

514
00:28:45,860 --> 00:28:47,100
So many years have passed,

515
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:48,340
and your son has grown up.

516
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:51,380
I thought you wouldn't
be blinded by love

517
00:28:51,380 --> 00:28:52,820
like a young man.

518
00:28:53,860 --> 00:28:54,620
You are now

519
00:28:55,140 --> 00:28:56,740
a mature man.

520
00:28:57,260 --> 00:28:59,140
You have to be responsible

521
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:00,740
for your marriage and family.

522
00:29:00,740 --> 00:29:01,660
What I need to do now

523
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:03,620
is to take my responsibility.

524
00:29:07,820 --> 00:29:08,780
I can't understand

525
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:10,820
why you hid

526
00:29:10,980 --> 00:29:12,340
that Le was born safely?

527
00:29:13,340 --> 00:29:14,300
You are also a mother.

528
00:29:17,660 --> 00:29:18,860
Ms. Tan

529
00:29:18,940 --> 00:29:20,700
is suffering
from severe prenatal depression.

530
00:29:20,860 --> 00:29:22,220
Here is her test report.

531
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:23,260
Please take a look.

532
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:30,980
Will it affect the fetus?

533
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:32,580
Prenatal depression

534
00:29:32,580 --> 00:29:34,700
may trigger more serious conditions,

535
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:35,860
including pessimistic thoughts.

536
00:29:36,100 --> 00:29:37,740
Some might have violent tendencies.

537
00:29:38,180 --> 00:29:38,860
Severely,

538
00:29:38,860 --> 00:29:41,780
a risk of impulsive, harmful behavior.

539
00:29:42,380 --> 00:29:43,700
All these are serious

540
00:29:43,700 --> 00:29:44,460
and dangerous.

541
00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:46,340
If she carries on like this,

542
00:29:46,620 --> 00:29:47,740
she could very well lose the baby.

543
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:49,260
So, I suggest you

544
00:29:49,580 --> 00:29:50,780
pay more attention to her emotions.

545
00:29:50,980 --> 00:29:51,940
Don't let things take their course.

546
00:29:52,260 --> 00:29:54,740
The best is to make her feel relaxed

547
00:29:55,220 --> 00:29:56,740
and meet those who make her feel safe.

548
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:57,660
That would help.

549
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:59,100
In short,

550
00:29:59,100 --> 00:30:00,420
you must not stimulate her.

551
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:03,940
Ms. Tan,

552
00:30:04,620 --> 00:30:05,220
if you don't eat,

553
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:06,380
you won't hold up,

554
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:07,860
and it's not good for the baby.

555
00:30:08,900 --> 00:30:10,180
I said I don't want to eat.

556
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:13,380
I heard from Feng Rui

557
00:30:13,620 --> 00:30:14,700
that fish heads are your favorite.

558
00:30:14,860 --> 00:30:16,300
I made some fish head soup for you.

559
00:30:16,460 --> 00:30:17,180
Please have a little.

560
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:25,820
Ms. Tan,

561
00:30:26,860 --> 00:30:27,940
I'll leave the soup on the table.

562
00:30:28,540 --> 00:30:29,260
I'll go back

563
00:30:29,260 --> 00:30:30,260
and come back tomorrow morning.

564
00:30:33,060 --> 00:30:33,460
Doctor,

565
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:34,740
it's not even eight months yet.

566
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:36,300
Too early for the baby to be born now.

567
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:37,900
Try to save the baby first,

568
00:30:38,300 --> 00:30:39,860
no matter how much money it costs.

569
00:30:40,460 --> 00:30:41,340
It's critical now.

570
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:42,100
Still talking about that?

571
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:44,100
Her placental abruption is dangerous.

572
00:30:45,980 --> 00:30:46,260
Then...

573
00:30:47,700 --> 00:30:48,060
Please

574
00:30:49,060 --> 00:30:50,980
ensure the child's safety.

575
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:55,020
The baby came suddenly.

576
00:30:57,260 --> 00:30:58,500
Her condition

577
00:30:59,860 --> 00:31:01,260
was unstable.

578
